list.abstract: influence，英语单词，影响，感化力，势力，权势。
《influence》是影视剧《长安十二时辰》海外推广曲，吉克隽逸演唱，Daryl K作词，Daryl K Calvin C作曲，发行于2019年8月7日。

yingyinNormal.en: The fel. Or at least it's influence.
yingyinNormal.zh: 是恶魔，或者至少是受他影响。

yingyinNormal.en: And of course, these influence us in many ways.
yingyinNormal.zh: 毋庸置疑，这对我们的影响表现在各方各面。

yingyinNormal.en: His soul has been poisoned by the influence of a dark master. The Shredder.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他的灵魂已经被黑暗老师的影响所毒害，施莱德。

yingyinNormal.en: Wow, Monica. What an amazing opportunity to influence dozens of people.
yingyinNormal.zh: 莫妮卡，这可是大好机会呢，你能影响到二、三十个人呢。

yingyinNormal.en: You are here to create history and influence what is to come. I don't think I can do it.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你是来创造历史并影响未来的。我觉得我做不到。

yingyinNormal.en: He does have this weird influence over her. Maybe he could talk her into taking the test.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他有时候的确能影响她，也许也能说服她去验孕。

yingyinNormal.en: Yeah. Tell me about it. I know, because I had a good influence. You're incomplete?
yingyinNormal.zh: 是啊，说的没错。我知道，因为有人给我带来好的影响。你不完整吗？

yingyinNormal.en: And Manny's been acting very suspicious lately I think that that older boy's a bad influence on him.
yingyinNormal.zh: 曼尼最近的举止很可疑，我觉得是那个男孩的坏影响。

yingyinNormal.en: And it's just intrinsically a problem, this imbalance in pop cultural influence. And I think so.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这在本质上是一个问题，流行文化影响的不平衡我认为也是如此。

yingyinNormal.en: Is she? What happens when you meet a good influence and they start to change you for the better?
yingyinNormal.zh: 是吗？当有人给你带来好的影响并开始把你变得更好，你会怎么样？

yingyinNormal.en: And this manipulation, in your opinion, did it constitute undue influence? Unfortunately, I think it did.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这种操纵，在你看来，是否构成了不正当影响呢？很不幸，我觉得是的。

yingyinNormal.en: And by the way, that anchor, the new anchor that you expect for Starbucks didn't just influence Starbucks.
yingyinNormal.zh: 如此一来“锚”,这个新“锚”，你所认可的星巴克咖啡的价格，其实不仅影响了星巴克。

yingyinNormal.en: You do have potential, Maya. What you don't have is a good influence. Quack! If he ever calls on me, you're finished. Quack.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你真的很有潜力，玛雅。你缺乏的是好的影响，嘎嘎！如果他关注我，你就完了。嘎。

yingyinNormal.en: I see hope. I see a unique voice who's learned to appreciate the influence of hope. Try not to lose that. I won't.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我看到了希望，我看到了一个独特的声音，她学会了欣赏希望的影响，不要丢了这一点。我不会、

yingyinNormal.en: I'm going to share some of my most important, overarching, life principles that influence how we approach everything that we do.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我要与各位分享我最重要，最突出的生活法则，这些法则能影响到我们待人处事的方式。

yingyinNormal.en: Shashi Tharoor called in a recent TED talk, the ability for a culture to tell a compelling story and influence others to fall in love with it.
yingyinNormal.zh: 沙希·塔鲁尔在不久前的一次TED演讲中说，它是一个文化，有能力讲出有说服力的故事，影响别人，让别人爱上它。

yingyinNormal.en: Pop culture, music, and the other methods of storytelling, movies, TV dramas, they are so key, and they do connect us, like me and Brian and do influence us, and inspire us.
yingyinNormal.zh: 流行文化，音乐，以及其他讲故事的方式，电影，电视剧，他们都是连结我们的关键，就像我和布莱恩，它们确实影响了我们，激励了我们。

yingyinNormal.en: Then in high school, I learnt that music wasn't just about connecting with others, like Brian and I were connected through music, it was a powerful tool of influence and inspiration.
yingyinNormal.zh: 然后在高中，我才知道了音乐，不仅是把我们联系在一起，就像布莱恩和我，通过音乐联系在一起，而且它还是影响和激励他人的有力工具。

yingyinNormal.en: Our founders realized that they could channel that wealth and influence for a greater good.
yingyinNormal.zh: 而我们的创建者意识到他们可以利用财富和影响力帮助更多的人。

yingyinNormal.en: New York touches not only the heavens with its mythic skyline, its influence radiates to every corner of the globe.
yingyinNormal.zh: 纽约不仅以神话般的高楼大厦见称，其影响力更遍及世界每一个角落。

sense_info_list.en: causing something without any direct or apparent effort

examination_example.sentence: Cultures without numbers also offer insight into the cognitive <highlight>influence</highlight> of particular numeric traditions.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 没有数字的文化也提供了对特定数字传统认知影响的洞察。

examination_example.sentence: A century ago, chemist Svante Arrhenius started one of the first debates over the potential for humans to <highlight>influence</highlight> the planet's climate.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 一个世纪前，化学家斯万特·阿伦尼乌斯(Svante Arrhenius)就人类影响地球气候的可能性展开了首次辩论。

examination_example.sentence: He hopes his acts of charity will <highlight>influence</highlight> others to spread positive actions in their own towns.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 他希望他的慈善行为能够影响其他人在自己的城镇传播积极的行动。

sense_info_list.en: the power to shape policy or ensure favorable treatment from someone

examination_example.sentence: Italy boasts more UNESCO World Heritage Sites than any other country in the world, granting it considerable power and <highlight>influence</highlight> within the organization.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 相比较世界上任何一个国家，意大利所拥有的联合国教科文组织(UNESCO)世界遗产最多，这使它在该组织中拥有相当大的权力和影响力。

examination_example.sentence: They have had a growing <highlight>influence</highlight> on the district.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 他们对该学区的影响越来越大。
